possible Queenside castling. C. After @@StartFEN@@rnbqkb1r/ppp1pp1p/3p1np1/8/
3PP3/2N5/PPP2PPP/R1BQKBNR w KQkq - 0 4@@EndFEN@@ 4.f4 Bg7 5.Nf3 O-O White also
has the aggressive option 6.e5 One crucial point: at various moments White has
