and the c-pawn is the most important one. It is the pawn that should attack
Black's pawn chain with c4-c5, opening files. A sample line in the King's
Indian is @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0
