stories. The right mindset about @@StartFEN@@rnbq1rk1/ppp1ppbp/3p1np1/8/3PP3/
2N2N2/PPP1BPPP/R1BQ1RK1 b - - 5 6@@EndFEN@@ 6...a6 is: we improve the ...Nc6/..
.e5 idea, and ...b5 is a good later option to resort to if White prevents ...
